<h2 id="70">7. Automatically sending shipping confirmations</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>You need to confirm UPG that you have sent the items to your customer before you will receive the customers payment from UPG. Set up an <a href="/en/automation/event-procedures">event procedure</a> to automatically send shipping confirmations when the outgoing items are booked.</p>
